{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-013","title":"生活用具","sectionId":"chapter-01","sectionTitle":"居家琐事会表达","pageStart":86,"pageEnd":89,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":21,"duplicateEntryCount":13,"pages":[{"number":86,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"13 生活用具"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"tool [tuːl]","headword":"tool"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.工具"},{"type":"note","text":"◎tool box工具箱"},{"type":"entry","text":"umbrella [ʌmˈbrelə]","headword":"umbrella"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.雨伞"},{"type":"entry","text":"earpick [ˈɪəpɪk]","headword":"earpick"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.掏耳勺"},{"type":"entry","text":"scissors [ˈsɪzəz]","headword":"scissors"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.剪刀"},{"type":"note","text":"◎nail scissors 指甲剪"},{"type":"entry","text":"knife [naɪf]","headword":"knife"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.刀"},{"type":"entry","text":"tape measure 卷尺","headword":"tape measure"},{"type":"entry","text":"caculator [ˈkælkjuleɪtə(r)]","headword":"caculator"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.计算器"}]},{"number":87,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"searchlight [ˈsɜːtʃlaɪt]","headword":"searchlight"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.探照灯"},{"type":"entry","text":"first-aid box 急救箱","headword":"first-aid box"},{"type":"entry","text":"funnel [ˈfʌnl]","headword":"funnel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.漏斗"},{"type":"note","text":"◎filter funnel过滤漏斗"},{"type":"entry","text":"trowel [ˈtraʊəl]","headword":"trowel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.泥铲"},{"type":"entry","text":"pruner [ˈpruːnə(r)]","headword":"pruner"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.修枝剪刀"},{"type":"entry","text":"crowbar [ˈkrəʊbɑː(r)]","headword":"crowbar"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.铁橇，撬棍"}]},{"number":88,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"grass trimmer 修草机","headword":"grass trimmer"},{"type":"entry","text":"appliance [əˈplaɪəns]","headword":"appliance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.用具；器具，电器"},{"type":"note","text":"◎appliance shop电器行"},{"type":"entry","text":"thermometer [θəˈmɒmɪtə(r)]","headword":"thermometer"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.温度计"},{"type":"entry","text":"hygrometer [haɪˈɡrɒmɪtə(r)]","headword":"hygrometer"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.湿度计"},{"type":"entry","text":"pointer multimetre 指针万用表","headword":"pointer multimetre"}]},{"number":89,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"electronic scale 电子秤","headword":"electronic scale"},{"type":"entry","text":"price computing scale 计价秤","headword":"price computing scale"},{"type":"entry","text":"compasses [ˈkʌmpəsɪs]","headword":"compasses"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.圆规"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词wheel"},{"type":"text","text":"1.我们中文中常管那种“很碍事”的人叫“电灯泡”，用英文表达就是"},{"type":"text","text":"the third wheel。如：I don't want to be the third wheel. （我不想当电灯"},{"type":"text","text":"泡。）"},{"type":"text","text":"2.还有一个关于wheel的习语也很常用：reinvent the wheel，字面意"},{"type":"text","text":"思是“再发明一次轮子”。对于早已经存在的东西，还要再发明一次，"},{"type":"text","text":"那完全是重复的工作，白费力气，所以reinvent the wheel就是指浪费资"},{"type":"text","text":"源与人力重复进行无意义的事。如：Go check if other people have done"},{"type":"text","text":"that already so you don't have to reinvent the wheel.（去查查看别人做过"},{"type":"text","text":"没有，这样你就不会白费力气了。）"}]}]}